Command line parser for rubyk using lemon (part of SQLite).

Files :

lexer.l
	This file contains the regexp rules for the tokenizer.

parser.y
	This file contains the grammar and actions to be executed when specific elements are found.
	
token.h
	Struct type definition. This type is used to pass the token from the lexer to the parser.
	
main.c
	Wrapper to create the test command line.
	
lemon.c
	Source code for lemon.
	
lempar.c
	Template for the parser that lemon generates.
	
	
That's it !